item.title: Founding of COVID19 infected age and source
item.description: Author Jiesen Cui Abstract Nowadays, we are facing a difficult time, because of COVID19. It’s important to know the most common age and source of infection of COVID19 so that we can try to avoid it. For the age group and most common way of getting infected of COVID19, we found it’s 20-59 and close contact. Introduction I selected the COVID19 toronto cases dataset to analyze. For now we are under a special situation because of COVID19, and it is really important to know the trends of COVID19 confirmed cases and some other information about it, such as the age group, source of infection.
